title: Fantasy Wallpaper Collection (190 pics)
description:
This is a collection of 190 of my favorite fantasy wallpapers that I've collected throughout the years.  

I apologize if any of them are repeats.  When I find a wallpaper I like I just add it to the folder.  I set my wallpapers in OS X to cycle every 15 minutes, so even if there are repeats, I don't notice.  I suggest you do the same!

If you'd like some previews, I can upload them, but the file is only ~190mb so it should download fairly quickly.
